dcterms:description: The Kelvins dataset contains conjunction data messages (CDMs) collected by the European Space Agency from 2015 to 2019, modified to anonymize sensitive information. It is used for predicting the final risk of collision for spacecraft.
dcterms:title: Kelvins dataset
